Use Case Name: Add/remove edit user profiles

Level: User-level

Description: Create and delete user profiles as well as change them

Precondition: There must be a parent/admin level user 

Triggering event: Change in role for a person within the house

Main flow:
Login from user applying change
Select profiles needed to be changed
Apply changes, ex: Stranger-> Guest, Guest-> Stranger
Grant/Remove relate premissions
Saves changes into the system

Extensions: 
1. User applying change isn't parent
Login
Select profiles needed to be changed
Apply changes
Changes refused
2. Automatic profile changes Guest/Children profile
Guest/Children enters or leaves the house
Optional timer started
Time frame expires
Guest/Children profile premissions granted/revoked

Postconditions:
Changes must be updated in the systems
